# Love wight
is an interaction designed fr 4 grown up and is intended to make them feel good toghter in the middle of the desert.


The interaction invlolve 2 round 60cm weigh that each one has a place for2 people to go on top.
in front of it there is a hughe 3 meter high heart the when you jump on the weight it translate your body weight into force applied on the heart.

The force pressed by the weight is converted into amount of lumination of the heart.

We will use sounds and light for each goal achived 
1. single person on one side.
2. two person on one side.
4. all 4 on each sides.


